<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ترتيبها ٩٧ ... سُورَةُ القَدْرِ ... آياتها ٥ ... مكية<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>الآية ... الكلمة ... معناها<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَنزَلْنَاهُ}</span> ... أَنْزَلْنَا القَرْآنَ جُمْلَةً وَاحِدَةً مِنَ اللَّوْحِ المَحْفُوظِ إِلَى بَيْتِ العِزَّةِ فِي السَّمَاءِ الدُّنْيَا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَيْلَةِ الْقَدْرِ}</span> ... لَيْلَةِ الشَّرَفِ، وَالعَظَمَةِ، وَكِتَابِ المَقَادِيرِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَالرُّوحُ}</span> ... جِبْرِيلُ - عليه السلام -.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَمْرٍ}</span> ... قَضَاءٍ قَدَّرَهُ اللهُ فِي تِلْكَ السَّنَةِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سَلَامٌ}</span> ... أَمْنٌ، وَسَلَامَةٌ، وَتَسْلِيمٌ مِنَ المَلَائِكَةِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>